Object_Definition: create view vw_user_print_logs as select u.user_id, u.user_name, u.full_name as user_full_name, p.server_name as printer_server_name, p.printer_name, p.display_name as printer_display_name, p.location as printer_location, pul.* from tbl_printer_usage_log pul inner join tbl_printer p on pul.printer_id = p.printer_id inner join tbl_user u on pul.used_by_user_id = u.user_id
